reemergence and recirculation of past strains that as such have advantage over decreasing host herd immunity against them;
  
  
    

unexplained genetic conservation found from time to time within IAV genomes or genes, in contradiction to the expected genetic drift biomolecular clock (annual rate of nucleotide substitutions).
